text: Nicole "Nikki" Reed (born May 17 1988) is an American movie actress. She has been featured mostly in independent movies. She was first brought to fame in 2003 with Thirteen. Reed was born in Los Angeles, California. She is of Ashkenazi Jewish, Cherokee Native American, English, French, German, Irish, Italian, Scottish, Swiss and Welsh descent. ==References== Category:Actors from Los Angeles category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American child actors Category:Jewish American actors Category:Native American people Category:1988 births Category:Living people
